{"tid":634655,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"恆管2學生涉校內藏毒被捕","createTime":"2018-04-19T12:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T13:49:50.000Z","uid":101341,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f8386c6c329243af38a35b6278ca0ee32359565f","tid":634655,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:16:25.000Z","msg":"恆生管理學院有2名學生涉嫌在校內藏毒，在職員報案後，警方到學校宿舍調查，拘捕該2名學生。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，恆生管理學院在本月12日（上周四）凌晨，有學生在校內懷疑吸毒，被警方拘捕。警方發言人回覆本報查詢時表示，本月12日凌晨約2時，接獲沙田行善里一院校職員報案，指懷疑有人在學生宿舍房間內吸食毒品。警員到場後，在現場檢獲少量懷疑大麻草及懷疑毒品吸食工具，並拘捕兩名分別21歲及22歲男子，涉嫌管有危險藥物。二人獲准保釋候查，須於下月底向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n恆管確認，在4月12日凌晨，校方發現學生宿舍房間有少量懷疑大麻草，即時報警處理。警方事後帶有關人士返警署協助調查。校方強調，非常重視學生操守及宿舍管理，對於任何涉嫌違規行為，都會嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學人講讀書喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"82abde4dede1861414aa4729e1bc8b9fd73c8ede","tid":634655,"uid":84646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"好 Chill<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ffd020b04e91cd5cc864ddc3060b716f45ee32","tid":634655,"uid":100347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"話大麻冇問題班冚家鏟幾時去警署門口聲援人？"},{"pid":"98997aa2df4a7df6b9a4068a9214707573d3050b","tid":634655,"uid":101341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"恆大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eec33e7efed5286bc7cd9c684396d8e6d8a0f0a","tid":634655,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"連登道友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41dec4b9686fe0e88a0